DISCLAIMER FOR FINANCIAL USE

TradeGuard X is a research and educational prototype built for a
hackathon. It is NOT intended for use with real financial assets or
in production trading environments.

  - The Alpaca integration uses Paper Trading only (simulated funds)
  - No real money is involved in any demo or prototype flow
  - The authors accept no liability for financial decisions made
    using or inspired by this software

Use in any live trading environment is entirely at the user's own risk.

